{"type":"message","id":"30e16f33","parentId":"54f472f7","timestamp":"2026-02-18T20:47:09.468Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Drafting the Response**\n\nI've dispatched the initial message, and now the focus shifts to crafting a thoughtful reply for Ireneo. I'm considering the best way to address his points, aiming for clarity and precision in my response. I'm aiming for a concise yet informative reply.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>Pronto, Irineu! Já mandei um \"Oi\" pro Franklin lá no Telegram pra ele ver que a prosa tá tinindo. [[reply_to_current]]</final>","textSignature":"Ck0Bjz1rX7izwFzVOt+kNMZNqVqGtc6xOUWo213iENdwY7YNIqvMNrEZWxd6dz7wqoZZJuaz7Qwlu/j84xJ0EUogfCnGk9t+GFJ1sybUhg=="}],"api":"google-gemini-cli","provider":"google-gemini-cli","model":"gemini-3-flash-preview","usage":{"input":2621,"output":54,"cacheRead":157846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":160521,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771447626713}}
