o commit but untracked files present (use \"git add\" to track)\n-rw-r--r-- 1 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 3708 Feb 18 20:58 MEMORY.md\n\nmemory/:\ntotal 60\ndrwxr-xr-x  7 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 4096 Feb 18 20:58 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 15 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 4096 Feb 18 20:58 ..\n-rw-r--r--  1 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo  153 Feb 18 20:58 2026-02-17-2208.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo  153 Feb 18 20:58 2026-02-18-1208.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo  153 Feb 18 20:58 2026-02-18-2012.md\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 4096 Feb 18 20:58 aparicio-funes\n-rw-r--r--  1 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 1266 Feb 18 20:58 corinthians.md\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 4096 Feb 18 20:58 daily\n-rw-r--r--  1 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 3205 Feb 18 20:58 diretrizes-editoriais.md\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 4096 Feb 18 20:58 familia-baldo\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 4096 Feb 18 20:58 prosa\n-rw-r--r--  1 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 6094 Feb 18 20:58 rascunho-vovo-franquilim.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 1678 Feb 18 20:58 rolim-de-moura.md\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 franklinbaldo franklinbaldo 4096 Feb 18 20:58 stats\n1d44fa1 chore: sync state","cwd":"/home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/workspace-aparicio"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771448299697}}
